  "text": ", generated by z andz with commutation relation zz = q \u22122z z \u2212 q \u22122 + 1 and involution z * =z with q real and nonzero (see [CITATION_1] ). The algebra C q [D] is Z graded, by z = 1 and z = \u22121. Putting w = 1 \u2212zz, we have zw = q \u22122 wz andzw = q 2 wz, so for any polynomial p(w)",
